query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id,
  pwi.productName,
  pwi.productSku,
  pr.pickingOrderId,
  po.customerOrderNumber
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
LEFT JOIN pickingReservations pr ON pwi.productId = pr.productId
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON pr.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = (SELECT id FROM pickingWaves ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1)
LIMIT 5;
